body_html: I'm sorry that nobody has answered on stackoverflow yet, but that is really the correct forum for this kind of usage question. Have you tried printing out the values of intermediate tensors e.g. h_conv1, h_conv2, h_pool, h_drop1? That should show you the shapes of all of them and help you understand where the tensor of size 313600 is coming from.
